    "description": "<strong>时间就是蜂蜜是一款温馨的放置游戏，你可以收集并照顾超过150种不同类型的蜜蜂。每只蜜蜂都有独特的外观，并能提升你的蜂蜜产量和收益。解锁并自定义蜂巢，然后升级以完成你的蜜蜂收藏，包括特殊的金色蜜蜂。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁和发现独特的蜜蜂</h2>发现超过<strong>150种独特的蜜蜂</strong>，每种蜜蜂都有可爱的外观和能够提升收益的属性！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/13f98925e988068fd66336794b4db830.poster.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/13f98925e988068fd66336794b4db830.webm?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >喂养你的蜜蜂</h2>用爱心和关怀来<strong>喂养你的蜜蜂</strong>。<strong>看着你的蜂巢越来越大</strong>，享受它们为你带来的蜂蜜作为奖励。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/798eaeee11c08295711d367aeaaad869.poster.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/798eaeee11c08295711d367aeaaad869.webm?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/798eaeee11c08295711d367aeaaad869.mp4?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义你的蜜蜂</h2>打开配件包以<strong>收集配件</strong>，你可以用它们来<strong>自定义和个性化你的蜜蜂。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/0f5807dd0757762454ea3cf999ee869e.poster.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/0f5807dd0757762454ea3cf999ee869e.webm?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/0f5807dd0757762454ea3cf999ee869e.mp4?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义你的蜂巢</h2>选择地面和蜂巢的颜色，添加贴纸，<strong>让你的蜂巢独一无二。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/80293596fb7819fdfe5133c565a1ce3b.poster.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/80293596fb7819fdfe5133c565a1ce3b.webm?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/80293596fb7819fdfe5133c565a1ce3b.mp4?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感谢</h2><strong>非常感谢你支持我的第一款Steam游戏！作为一名独立开发者，你的关注对我意义重大。我真心感谢每一个试玩游戏或将其添加到愿望单中的人。</strong>",
